title: 2021 T1 - T2 (2012) (Sosich) cbr
description:
A column of armed cars penetrates the autonomous territory of Detroit, Michigan. In only a few minutes, the American soldiers come under enemy fire and their patrol is completely decimated. Four child soldiers extricate themselves from the battlefield ruins. Their weapons: supernatural powers, the use of which makes them age prematurely. Their mission before dying of old age: find and execute Ike Mercy, the elusive leader of the insurgent city.

enjoy
